title: Hyeongseop X Euiwoong
text:
Hyeongseop X Euiwoong (Korean: 형섭x의웅) is a South Korean duo formed by Yuehua Entertainment. The duo, composed of Ahn Hyeongseop and Lee Euiwoong, previously participated in Produce 101 Season 2. They debuted on November 2, 2017, with the single "It Will Be Good". Both of Hyeongseop and Euiwoong re-debuted in Yuehua's boy group Tempest on March 2, 2022.
